  "body": "Assumes network-level block reward and mining beneficiary has already been complete for IBFT2.\n===\n\nExtend the transitions section of the Genesis file to allow the mining beneficiary and/or the block reward to be changed at any block.\n\nThis will mean the \"Transitions\" will need to be applied to an existing ProtocolSchedule by:\n* Inserting a new milestone at the specified block (but otherwise identical to the preceding milestone), and * modify the existing behaviour of all latter milestones with the change specified in the transition.",
